今年这些大电影项目全部取消https://www.nme.com/news/film/这些-big-movie-projects-have-all-been-cancelled-this-year-3548827?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=这些-big-movie-projects-今年全部取消Rhian DalySat, 25 Nov 2023 09:00:10 +0000 Film NewsNewsDisneyMarvel Cinematic UniverseStar Wars https://www.nme.com/?p=3548827 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/star-wars-logo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="星球大战" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/star-wars-logo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/star-wars-logo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/star-wars-logo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/star-wars-logo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/star-wars-logo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/star-wars-logo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一些备受期待的电影未能熬过 2023 年</p><p>这篇文章<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/these-big-movie-projects-have-all-been-cancelled-this-year-3548827">《这些大电影项目今年全部被取消》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/star-wars-logo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="星球大战" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/star-wars-logo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/star-wars-logo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/star-wars-logo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/star-wars-logo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/star-wars-logo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/star-wars-logo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2023 年，许多大型电影项目被取消，电影公司重新考虑他们的计划，SAG-AFTRA 和 WGA 罢工震动了整个行业。</p><p>许多电影和电视节目都因罢工而被推迟或受到某种程度的影响，编剧、演员和工作人员都在争取更好的工作保护。</p><p>虽然很多电影都经受住了这场风暴和不断发展的行业，但并不是每个项目都如此幸运。以下是今年迄今为止已被取消的电影。</p><h2> <strong>2023 年哪些电影被取消？</strong></h2><h3><strong>凯文·费奇的未命名<em>星球大战</em>电影</strong></h3><figure id="attachment_3548833" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3548833" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3548833" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/kevin-feige-star-wars.jpg" alt="凯文·费奇" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/kevin-feige-star-wars.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/kevin-feige-star-wars-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/kevin-feige-star-wars-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/kevin-feige-star-wars-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/kevin-feige-star-wars-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/kevin-feige-star-wars-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3548833" class="wp-caption-text">凯文·费奇 图片来源：Alberto Rodriguez/Deadline via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/marvel-cinematic-universe">漫威</a>老板凯文·费奇原计划带着他自己的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/star-wars"><em>星球大战</em></a>电影进入一个遥远的星系，但我们将不再看到他会对我们最喜欢的绝地武士做什么。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-marvels"><em>漫威</em></a>首映式上， <em>《ET》</em>被问及该项目是否仍在进行时，<a href="https://twitter.com/etnow/status/1722088080965038268" target="_blank" rel="noopener">费奇简洁地回答：“没有。”</a>与此同时， <a href="https://variety.com/2023/film/news/star-wars-kevin-feige-patty-jenkins-movies-shelved-1235545774/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《综艺》杂志</em></a>的一份报告证实，这部电影“不再在卢卡斯影业积极开发中”。</p><h3><strong><em>盗贼中队</em></strong></h3><figure id="attachment_3548832" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3548832" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3548832" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/patty-jenkins-star-wars.jpg" alt="帕蒂·詹金斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/patty-jenkins-star-wars.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/patty-jenkins-star-wars-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/patty-jenkins-star-wars-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/patty-jenkins-star-wars-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/patty-jenkins-star-wars-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/patty-jenkins-star-wars-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3548832" class="wp-caption-text">帕蒂·詹金斯 图片来源：Frazer Harrison/Getty Images for ELLE</figcaption></figure><p>另一位准备从超级英雄宇宙跳跃到星际宇宙的导演是<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wonder-woman"><em>《神奇女侠</em></a>》中的帕蒂·詹金斯。她的<em>《星球大战》</em>电影比费奇的电影发展得更进一步——以至于它有一个名字：<em>侠盗中队</em>。然而，这并不能帮助它保持活力，因为它被从<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/disney">迪士尼</a>的名单中删除了。詹金斯则表示，她仍在开发它，但不知道“它是否会发生”。</p><h3> <strong><em>Coyote VS Acme</em></strong> </h3><figure id="attachment_3548831" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3548831" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3548831" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/john-cena-coyote-vs-acme.jpg" alt="约翰·塞纳" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/john-cena-coyote-vs-acme.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/john-cena-coyote-vs-acme-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/john-cena-coyote-vs-acme-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/john-cena-coyote-vs-acme-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/john-cena-coyote-vs-acme-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/john-cena-coyote-vs-acme-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3548831" class="wp-caption-text">约翰·塞纳 图片来源：Jason Mendez/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>约翰·塞纳 (John Cena) 执导的《狼大战<em>阿克米》(Coyote vs Acme)</em>一路顺利完成制作和试映，但最终被华纳搁置。这部电影将动画与真人结合起来，根据 30 多年前发表在《<em>纽约客》</em>上的一篇讽刺文章改编，讲述了卡通人物怀尔·E·狼 (Wile E. Coyote) 在其产品未能提供帮助后聘请广告牌律师起诉 Acme 的故事。他是最好的走鹃。华纳的一位发言人告诉<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/john-cena-coyote-vs-acme-movie-shelved-1235643235/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《好莱坞报道》，</em></a>做出这一决定是因为该工作室“将其全球战略转向专注于院线发行”。</p><h3><strong><em>福</em></strong></h3><figure id="attachment_3548830" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3548830" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3548830" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aziz-ansari-good-fortune.jpg" alt="阿齐兹·安萨里" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aziz-ansari-good-fortune.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aziz-ansari-good-fortune-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aziz-ansari-good-fortune-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aziz-ansari-good-fortune-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aziz-ansari-good-fortune-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/aziz-ansari-good-fortune-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3548830" class="wp-caption-text">阿齐兹·安萨里 (Aziz Ansari) 图片来源：Brian Feinzimer/Variety via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>阿齐兹·安萨里将执导并主演这部喜剧，塞斯·罗根和基努·里维斯也签约出演。然而，当编剧罢工时，洛杉矶韩国城的制作受到了纠察，该项目最终被无限期关闭。它有可能在未来复活，但自五月份以来没有任何消息对该项目来说并不是一个好兆头。</p><p>这篇文章<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/these-big-movie-projects-have-all-been-cancelled-this-year-3548827">《这些大电影项目今年全部被取消》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
